{
  "3164710": {
    "name": "Quality Dreams, Reasonably Priced",
    "steam_appid": 3164710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/f0d83d1f8ee822b6d312d37b6de0284f.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1560 height=760 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work at a body modification clinic in a cyberpunk tower-city. Play as Jin, a salesperson advising clients on mods. Making little money aside from what you earn on commission, save up enough to afford your sick rabbit's surgery in two weeks. Watch your decisions ripple through the lives of each character you meet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/0ae6832df1e3287d3104782a62fc9c5e.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1560 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clients from all walks of life visit the clinic. As you speak with them and uncover their secrets, you'll have to decide if they should get the mods they seek. Choose between morals and your bottom line, and impact the client’s future as well as your own. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each decision you make ripples out into the world, changing the lives of your clients and coworkers. Watch the results of your actions play out in a responsive world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/af8d745890e73ed7cd2a340a11f7e20f.avif?t=1766894410\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras_big/af8d745890e73ed7cd2a340a11f7e20f.avif?t=1766894410 width=1560 height=710 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/c48ab950adc7578b5b1ffb3521f2d040.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1560 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you recommend the procedure, you will have the opportunity to upsell your clients. Decide which upsell options and sales tactics work best to win over your client. Be careful not to push too hard though—it may cause resentment and impact your work reviews.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/ba4bb56bc871eb555828e4493c90ba0d.poster.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/ba4bb56bc871eb555828e4493c90ba0d.webm?t=1766894410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/ba4bb56bc871eb555828e4493c90ba0d.mp4?t=1766894410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/3fc353927aa1a9d17400b84cc90b6bd7.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1560 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through your conversations with characters, you may develop positive or negative relationships with them. Learn about your clients and coworkers in wide-ranging dialogues. Impact their lives through your words and actions, then experience how they impact your life in return.   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/b248f30663c8328aa01f65f13dfd5e77.avif?t=1766894410\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras_big/b248f30663c8328aa01f65f13dfd5e77.avif?t=1766894410 width=1560 height=710 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/4cb5e4f3842251d02eaa4e55ec8cd2f8.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1560 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/2ad2b38cff8c1f267e52f01633772290.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1560 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time Jin speaks, you decide what they say. Figure out which options lead to the information or outcomes you seek. Use words to shape what kind of person Jin becomes over the course of the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/3679e887c6d7c7554d7c62209eb6e4ad.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1560 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of each day, budget your finances and decide what luxuries you want to spend on (if any). Plan and allocate money to ensure you have enough saved up to afford your rabbit’s surgery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/833b19b8d0e7fa2c66a40405dec3e30a.poster.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/833b19b8d0e7fa2c66a40405dec3e30a.webm?t=1766894410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/833b19b8d0e7fa2c66a40405dec3e30a.mp4?t=1766894410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/fb3d69f6cda6cad24aa4035d69bd1574.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1560 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you may unlock keepsakes from various characters. Use them to decorate your home or sell them to try and meet your savings goals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164710/extras/db2cae156dd2fde8b5f9ad97eb747330.avif?t=1766894410\" width=1560 height=760 /></span></p>",
